My guys from the Kampong Chhnang Orphanage 😁

Can't really put into words what our trip to #Cambodia was like, but I'm just so grateful to have been a part of it. Thank you @carlibel for allowing me to be by your side (and film ☺️) for this life-changing experience. These past few days have been some of the best we've ever had together. So many smiles. So much genuinity. So much to take away and learn from. You may look up to me because I'm tall but I'd be lying if I didn't say I'm the one who looks up to you. You've changed so many lives for the better. I have more respect for you than this world knows what to do with. And thank you @wah_foundation for your continued dedication in creating a healthier way of life for these kids and their environment. 🙏 Next stop: Indonesia 🇰🇭✈️🇮🇩
Beauty (by Carli Bybel) and the Beast 👹👰🏻
